---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Pricing | ClubShed Football Equipment Tracker';
const description = 'Free for one team, 30 items, 3 coaches. €15.99/month for unlimited. No card required to start.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="pricing-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="tag">Pricing</span>
      <h1 class="display">Honest pricing.<br />About the price of one lost football a month.</h1>
      <p class="pricing-lede">No "contact sales" tiers. No seat-based pricing that punishes you for having more coaches. One paid plan that covers your whole club.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="plans">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="plans__grid">

        <div class="plan">
          <div class="plan__head">
            <h2 class="display">Free</h2>
            <p class="plan__sub">For a single team or a club testing the water.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="plan__price">
            <span class="plan__amount">€0</span>
            <span class="plan__period">forever</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan__features">
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> 1 team</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Up to 30 equipment items</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Up to 3 coaches</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Photo inventory</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Check-in / check-out log</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Email return reminders</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Mobile-friendly</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.clubshed.pro/signup" class="btn btn--ghost plan__cta">Start free</a>
          <p class="plan__finer">No card required. Stay free forever if it works for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="plan plan--featured">
          <div class="plan__badge">Recommended</div>
          <div class="plan__head">
            <h2 class="display">Club</h2>
            <p class="plan__sub">For grassroots and amateur clubs that mean it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="plan__price">
            <span class="plan__amount">€15.99</span>
            <span class="plan__period">/ month, billed monthly</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan__features">
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Unlimited teams</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Unlimited equipment items</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> QR code stickers (print at home)</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Coach allocations and handovers</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Custom categories and locations</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> End-of-season PDF report</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Automatic email reminders for overdue gear</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Multiple admins</li>
            <li><span class="tick">✓</span> Priority support (direct email)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.clubshed.pro/signup?plan=club" class="btn btn--accent plan__cta">Start 14-day trial</a>
          <p class="plan__finer">14 days of paid features free. No card required. Cancel anytime.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="display">Honest answers.</h2>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>What happens when the 14-day trial ends?</h3>
        <p>If you've added a card, the Club plan kicks in at €15.99/month. If you haven't, your account rolls back to the Free plan and you keep all your data. Items beyond the 30-item limit stay visible but become read-only until you upgrade or delete some. Nothing is ever deleted. No surprise charges.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>Why €15.99 and not €49 or €99?</h3>
        <p>Because grassroots clubs aren't enterprise. Most of you are run by volunteers who pay for things out of their own pocket and claim it back, sometimes. €15.99 is the price a volunteer can sign up for without a committee vote.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>Can I import from a spreadsheet?</h3>
        <p>Yes, CSV import is in the Club plan. But honestly, most clubs are better off starting fresh with photos. Your spreadsheet probably has 47 entries that say "ball" anyway.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>Do you replace Spond or Crossbar?</h3>
        <p>No. ClubShed is the equipment piece those tools handle badly. Keep using whatever you use for member admin and payments. ClubShed sits next to it for kit and gear.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>What if I run a bigger club, like 500+ players?</h3>
        <p>The €15.99 plan still covers you. If you ever need bulk features (multi-site, integrations, etc), email me and we'll figure something out.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>Will the price go up?</h3>
        <p>For new customers, maybe. For anyone who signs up at €15.99, the price stays €15.99 for as long as you keep your subscription active. That's the deal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3>How do I cancel?</h3>
        <p>One button in your account. No email asking why, no retention call. If ClubShed isn't working for you, that's on us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="final-cta-pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="display">Try it. Worst case, you waste 10 minutes.</h2>
      <a href="https://app.clubshed.pro/signup" class="btn btn--accent">Start free</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .pricing-hero {
    padding-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-hero .tag {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-hero h1 {
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pricing-lede {
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .plans__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .plans__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .plan {
    background: var(--chalk-warm);
    border: 2px solid var(--asphalt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .plan--featured {
    background: var(--pitch-deep);
    color: var(--chalk);
    border-color: var(--pitch-deep);
    transform: translateY(-12px);
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--kit-orange);
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .plan--featured {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  .plan__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--kit-orange);
    color: var(--chalk);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .plan__head h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .plan__sub {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .plan__price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .plan__amount {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .plan__period {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .plan__features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .plan__features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tick {
    color: var(--kit-orange);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .plan--featured .tick {
    color: var(--kit-orange-soft);
  }

  .plan__cta {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .plan--featured .plan__cta {
    color: var(--chalk);
    border-color: var(--kit-orange);
    background: var(--kit-orange);
  }

  .plan__finer {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    opacity: 0.65;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .faq__item {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .faq__item h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .faq__item p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .final-cta-pricing {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--chalk-warm);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--asphalt);
  }

  .final-cta-pricing h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
